original: Laurell, Theodor, läroverksadjunkt, Karlshamn, f. 9/1/05 i Aspö, Södermani. 1., av kyrkoh. Gustaf L. o. Signe Trönnberg. G. 37 m. Elsa Wiman. — Studrex. i Strängnäs 24, teol. fil. ex. i Upps. 26, teol. kand. 30, prästex. o. prästv. i Västerås 30. V. kommin. i Ludvika 31, past radj. i By 31-33, v. kommin. i Horndal 33, v. pastor i Irsta o. Badelunda 33-35, kommin. i Ängsö 35, adj. i kristend. o. modersm. v. Karlshamns samrealsk. sed. 44. Ordf. i Karlshamns kyrkobrödrakår sed. 45 0. i Lärov:lär. riksförb. lokalfören. v. komm. gymn. o. samrealsk. i Karlshamn sed. 46. Skr.: Beskrivning över Ängsö kyrka, Västerås stift (40, 2. uppl. 42).
translated: Laurell, Theodor, secondary school teacher, Karlshamn, b. 9/1/05 in Aspö, Södermani. 1st, of Rev. Gustaf L. and Signe Trönnberg. Married in 1937 to Elsa Wiman. - Studied at Strängnäs until 1924, received a Bachelor of Theology degree from Uppsala in 1926, a Master of Theology degree in 1930, and passed the examinations to be ordained as a priest in Västerås in 1930. Served as a deputy vicar in Ludvika from 1931, as a pastor at By from 1931 to 1933, as a deputy vicar in Horndal from 1933, as a vicar in Irsta and Badelunda from 1933 to 1935, as a curate in Ängsö from 1935, and as a teacher of Christian studies and the Swedish language at Karlshamn secondary school since 1944. Chairman of the Karlshamn church brotherhood since 1945 and of the Local Association of the National Union of Teachers in Gymnasium and Secondary School in Karlshamn since 1946. Published: Description of Ängsö Church, Västerås Diocese (40, 2nd edition 42).
